{"type":"message","id":"2f6479af","parentId":"f6c5337a","timestamp":"2026-03-25T00:22:52.109Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_am0A9ArdiDP8RDMLpqiV7JA8|fc_0b41fd20182e28500169c32adecca08191907c1d6e61a20220","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b8b184ac-d733-4a46-a6f3-dbe3877d1496\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-openclaw-git-backup\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774361618484,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774361618484,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"30 22 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Run the script `C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\scripts\\\\daily-backup-to-branch.cmd` on the host. It should perform a brute-force git backup of `C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw` to branch `backup`. After running it, report success or the exact failure in one short message. Do not modify the script unless execution fails and the fix is obvious.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 600\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774409400000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"03b29602-b584-4ec0-9241-b0d74393cc82\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-atlas-os-review\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774388052968,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774388052968,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Review the Notion page 'Atlas OS' using the local Notion integration available on this machine. Summarize what is active, blocked, and next. Then coordinate with the relevant sub-agents only when useful based on the board state. Keep it concise and action-oriented. If nothing needs intervention, send a short no-op summary.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774443600000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"1b498596-f8f3-4976-89ea-07a8edda91dc\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:tui-ff9e3c06-d72f-4309-808e-17050e7b293f\",\n      \"name\": \"Atlas OS review - morning\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774392410001,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774392410001,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"session:agent:main:tui-ff9e3c06-d72f-4309-808e-17050e7b293f\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Revisa la página de Notion 'Atlas OS' y úsala como dashboard operativo. Haz una revisión ejecutiva de mañana: 1) identifica tareas activas, listas, bloqueadas, waiting y hechas; 2) detecta si alguna tarea se terminó o cambió de estado; 3) produce un análisis breve de prioridades, cuellos de botella y siguientes pasos; 4) con base en los pendientes, coordina y ordena a los subagentes correctos para avanzar en sus actividades cuando aplique; 5) responde al usuario con un resumen accionable en español, directo y práctico. No hagas acciones destructivas en Notion. Si hay restricciones de un subagente o dudas operativas, respétalas y menciona la limitación.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 1800\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774443600000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"b824f7b0-7497-4984-b0ff-d1bd45539f3c\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"daily-email-review-and-whatsapp-reminder\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774390465819,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774390767591,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 8 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Review the Gmail inbox of atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com using gog. Look for forwarded messages from Gustavo's personal email, pending items for today, and near-term deadlines. Organize the relevant items into the appropriate shared calendar flow for Gustavo by citing/scheduling what applies toward toledo970501@gmail.com, then send Gustavo a concise WhatsApp reminder to +573183718246 with what he has pending today and any nearby deadlines. Include important context if relevant. Example current context: he has 3 days from 2026-03-24 to complete a ZooLATECH challenge. Be concise and practical.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774443600000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"3911daa5-65a3-4fca-b14a-0ec664a6cb10\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:tui-ff9e3c06-d72f-4309-808e-17050e7b293f\",\n      \"name\": \"Atlas OS review - midday\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774392416651,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774392416651,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 12 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"session:agent:main:tui-ff9e3c06-d72f-4309-808e-17050e7b293f\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Revisa la página de Notion 'Atlas OS' y úsala como dashboard operativo. Haz una revisión ejecutiva de mediodía: 1) identifica tareas activas, listas, bloqueadas, waiting y hechas; 2) detecta si alguna tarea se terminó o cambió de estado; 3) produce un análisis breve de prioridades, cuellos de botella y siguientes pasos; 4) con base en los pendientes, coordina y ordena a los subagentes correctos para avanzar en sus actividades cuando aplique; 5) responde al usuario con un resumen accionable en español, directo y práctico. No hagas acciones destructivas en Notion. Si hay restricciones de un subagente o dudas operativas, respétalas y menciona la limitación.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 1800\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774458000000\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"8157ed89-ee52-482d-a791-31181c4fff11\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:main\",\n      \"name\": \"evening-email-review-and-calendar-check\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774390767598,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774396832632,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 19 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Review the Gmail inbox of atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com using gog for pending items, unresolved tasks, and near-term deadlines. Organize relevant items into the appropriate shared calendar flow for Gustavo by citing/scheduling what applies toward toledo970501@gmail.com, then send Gustavo a concise WhatsApp reminder to +573183718246 with the evening paneo: what is still pending, what rolls into tomorrow, and what deadlines are close. Keep it concise and practical.\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 900\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774483200000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1774396800021,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 32611,\n        \"lastDelivered\": true,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"delivered\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"af05158b-5c6f-4bea-b93d-38366dea639f\",\n      \"agentId\": \"main\",\n      \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:tui-ff9e3c06-d72f-4309-808e-17050e7b293f\",\n      \"name\": \"Atlas OS review - end of day\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1774392423014,\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1774397735212,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 19 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"America/Bogota\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"session:agent:main:tui-ff9e3c06-d72f-4309-808e-17050e7b293f\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"Revisa la página de Notion 'Atlas OS' y úsala como dashboard operativo. Haz una revisión ejecutiva de cierre de jornada: 1) identifica tareas activas, listas, bloqueadas, waiting y hechas; 2) detecta si alguna tarea se terminó o cambió de estado; 3) produce un análisis breve de prioridades, cuellos de botella y siguientes pasos; 4) con base en los pendientes, coordina y ordena a los agentes responsables correctos para avanzar en sus actividades usando coordinación cross-agent cuando aplique; 5) si una tarea requiere acción inmediata de un agente específico (por ejemplo Ares en Smart Project), envíale la coordinación directamente a su sesión correspondiente; 6) responde al usuario con un resumen accionable en español, directo y práctico, incluyendo qué agentes fueron coordinados. No hagas acciones destructivas en Notion. Si un agente tiene dudas o se traba, ayúdalo; si hace falta aprobación, escala a Gustavo por WhatsApp.\",