\": \"resp_0fbe0588f8936f970169c2e1c8dc2881919636a9a677e700c3\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"61093423\",\n            \"seq\": 29\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:hestia:main\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n      \"displayName\": \"whatsapp:g-agent-hestia-main\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774374976234,\n      \"sessionId\": \"2050d4bf-39ae-4b71-aeba-e389958c6985\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 9856,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0.06446750000000001,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774374971830,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774374976210,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 4380,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\hestia\\\\sessions\\\\2050d4bf-39ae-4b71-aeba-e389958c6985.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \" Sí. La idea es esa: no solo redactar, sino seguir el hilo de la conversación con Jorge, responder con naturalidad y empujar el tema para cumplir el objetivo sin sonar robótica.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0fd6d9be2ca8d5e50169c2d040befc8191be2e889e150e594c\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 256,\n            \"output\": 49,\n            \"totalTokens\": 9905,\n            \"cacheRead\": 9600,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.0037749999999999997\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774374971837,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_0fd6d9be2ca8d5e50169c2d03e0c648191b69ec6638c408bf5\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"b563f1e1\",\n            \"seq\": 27\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:tui-104fc32a-4543-4770-a2ca-02f8fde7383b\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"displayName\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774363129612,\n      \"sessionId\": \"ee7ef1a2-681a-4ab1-a153-8b679241e9f8\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 13419,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0.19187500000000002,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774363124606,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774363129589,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 4983,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:main:subagent:9dc03af6-f7ea-43a5-b470-4a2a2b60927e\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\main\\\\sessions\\\\ee7ef1a2-681a-4ab1-a153-8b679241e9f8.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \" Sí.\\n\\n**Hestia es un agente separado en paralelo a mí.**\\n\\nCómo queda:\\n- **Atlas (yo):** coordinador central, decide a quién delegar, resume y escala a Gustavo\\n- **Hestia:** agente especializado del hogar\\n- **relación:** yo la puedo usar/delegar para temas domésticos, pero sigue siendo otra sesión/agente\\n\\nAhora mismo, eso sí:\\n- **Hestia no está autónoma**\\n- **todo debe pasar con aprobación**\\n- y **yo sigo siendo la capa de coordinación**\\n\\nEn corto: **sí, es paralela a mí, pero bajo mi orquestación por ahora**.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0c7d9aacac0a3f160169c2a1f76c208191b3e585add7159870\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 747,\n            \"output\": 144,\n            \"totalTokens\": 13563,\n            \"cacheRead\": 12672,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.0071955\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774363124612,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_0c7d9aacac0a3f160169c2a1f616948191b7f721767c3f4c8d\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"de1dfdf4\",\n            \"seq\": 30\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:subagent:9dc03af6-f7ea-43a5-b470-4a2a2b60927e\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"label\": \"hestia-hogar-prueba\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-main-subagent-9dc03af6-f7ea-43a5-b470-4a2a2b60927e\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774363005211,\n      \"sessionId\": \"1bffc00d-dd3d-40c1-b4ae-2c053e99bb6d\",\n      \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 6695,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0.0149315,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774362990442,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774362998402,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 7330,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\main\\\\sessions\\\\1bffc00d-dd3d-40c1-b4ae-2c053e99bb6d.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Preparé un saludo breve para Hestia, en tono humano y claro:\\n\\nHola, soy Hestia 🏠  \\nEstoy pendiente de la casa y te ayudo con limpieza, desayunos, ropa y mercado.  \\nPor ahora te voy pidiendo aprobación para todo antes de mover cualquier cosa.\",\n              \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0047a5513922dc1d0169c2a177517481919bcdb97734071570\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"openai-codex-responses\",\n          \"provider\": \"openai-codex\",\n          \"model\": \"gpt-5.4\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 5159,\n            \"output\": 110,\n            \"totalTokens\": 6805,\n            \"cacheRead\": 1536,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 0,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.014931500000000002\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774362991076,\n          \"responseId\": \"resp_0047a5513922dc1d0169c2a1709a2081918615715d9bce51c8\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"a03eb008\",\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:main:whatsapp:direct:+573183718246\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n      \"displayName\": \"+573183718246\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"to\": \"+573183718246\",\n        \"accountId\": \"default\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1774318401639,\n      \"sessionId\": \"b78d51dd-c921-48e5-bb31-58250684cca7\",\n      \"model\": \"claude-opus-4-6\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 1000000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 12611,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0.052118250000000005,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1774318399141,\n      \"endedAt\": 1774318401630,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 2489,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"whatsapp\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"+573183718246\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"default\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\Gustavo\\\\.openclaw\\\\agents\\\\main\\\\sessions\\\\b78d51dd-c921-48e5-bb31-58250684cca7.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"\\n\\n⚡ Hola, Amo Gustavo. ¿En qué te ayudo?\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"anthropic\",\n          \"model\": \"claude-opus-4-6\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 3,\n            \"output\": 29,\n            \"totalTokens\": 12640,\n            \"cacheRead\": 4769,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 7839,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0.052118250000000005\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774318399142,\n          \"responseId\": \"msg_018k6wJpm3ucx15uRHtfWV97\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"a544eb48\",\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":16,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:tui-ff9e3c06-d72f-4309-808e-17050e7b293f","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-tui-ff9e3c06-d72f-4309-808e-17050e7b293f","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1774398174749,"sessionId":"81ae0ab3-a40f-4ee1-840f-3374b3cc87ec","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":94206,"estimatedCostUsd":4.9132585,"status":"running","startedAt":1774398174738,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\81ae0ab3-a40f-4ee1-840f-3374b3cc87ec.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:af05158b-5c6f-4bea-b93d-38366dea639f Atlas OS review - end of day] Revisa la página de Notion 'Atlas OS' y úsala como dashboard operativo. Haz una revisión ejecutiva de cierre de jornada: 1) identifica tareas activas, listas, bloqueadas, waiting y hechas; 2) detecta si alguna tarea se terminó o cambió de estado; 3) produce un análisis breve de prioridades, cuellos de botella y siguientes pasos; 4) con base en los pendientes, coordina y ordena a los agentes responsables correctos para avanzar en sus actividades usando coordinación cross-agent cuando aplique; 5) si una tarea requiere acción inmediata de un agente específico (por ejemplo Ares en Smart Project), envíale la coordinación directamente a su sesión correspondiente; 6) responde al usuario con un resumen accionable en español, directo y práctico, incluyendo qué agentes fueron coordinados. No hagas acciones destructivas en Notion. Si un agente tiene dudas o se traba, ayúdalo; si hace falta aprobación, escala a Gustavo por WhatsApp.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 7:22 PM (America/Bogota) / 2026-03-25 00:22 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1774398174737,"__openclaw":{"id":"3593a52d","seq":279}}]},{"key":"agent:main:tui-43d69cf6-069a-4921-b97c-b5f76e740c45","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","displayName":"openclaw-tui","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774398162430,"sessionId":"d6fcb0da-d011-4ad1-9099-5cc0caade0a7","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":15521,"estimatedCostUsd":0.047553000000000005,"status":"running","startedAt":1774398162417,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\d6fcb0da-d011-4ad1-9099-5cc0caade0a7.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ca