:"unknown","label":"Cron: evening-email-review-and-calendar-check","displayName":"Cron: evening-email-review-and-calendar-check","updatedAt":1774396800168,"sessionId":"f44883d4-96b3-49c7-a2dc-25c89d81a640","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":10254,"estimatedCostUsd":0.040049,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\f44883d4-96b3-49c7-a2dc-25c89d81a640.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":""},{"type":"text","text":"No pude completar el paneo ni organizar nada en Calendar: el acceso de `gog` para `atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com` está roto.\n\nError al intentar leer Gmail:\n`invalid_grant: Token has been expired or revoked`\n\nImpacto:\n- Inbox: no revisado\n- Pendientes/no resueltos: no verificados\n- Deadlines cercanos: no verificados\n- Calendar hacia `toledo970501@gmail.com`: no actualizado\n- WhatsApp a `+573183718246`: no enviado por esta corrida\n\nAcción necesaria:\n- Reautenticar `gog` para `atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com`\n- Luego reejecutar este job\n\nDestino previsto del recordatorio:\n- Gustavo por WhatsApp en `+573183718246`","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_043b003fe40f4c1c0169c325a11f008191966bdb0b5c84d4af\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":270,"output":369,"totalTokens":10623,"cacheRead":9984,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.008706}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774396823953,"responseId":"resp_043b003fe40f4c1c0169c3259b78388191adb945ca28988a0d","__openclaw":{"id":"f55fba79","seq":10}}]},{"key":"agent:main:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","displayName":"heartbeat","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1774395860621,"sessionId":"8ce68dc4-7cc4-4942-baff-dfb71fd23df0","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":105118,"estimatedCostUsd":10.766992750000002,"status":"done","startedAt":1774395853422,"endedAt":1774395860609,"runtimeMs":7187,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\8ce68dc4-7cc4-4942-baff-dfb71fd23df0.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":" Sí. Ya quedó actualizado y guardado para futuras sesiones.\n\nLo nuevo que quedó recordado es:\n\n- usar `atlas.ia.agente@gmail.com` como inbox operativo\n- revisar correo **dos veces al día**\n  - **8:00 AM**\n  - **7:00 PM**\n- mandarte paneo por WhatsApp a:\n  - **`+573183718246`**\n- y además organizar/citar lo relevante en calendario hacia:\n  - **`toledo970501@gmail.com`**\n\nTambién quedó **commiteado** en memoria.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07843e13d03825ba0169c30e1625d48191a849c71293b7fab5\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":324,"output":124,"totalTokens":109120,"cacheRead":108672,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.029837999999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774390796792,"responseId":"resp_07843e13d03825ba0169c30e10cee0819184eb788d39786604","__openclaw":{"id":"f1d220c5","seq":670}}]},{"key":"agent:prometeo:whatsapp:group:120363407571517396@g.us","kind":"group","channel":"whatsapp","displayName":"whatsapp:g-tradelab","deliveryContext":{"channel":"whatsapp","to":"120363407571517396@g.us","accountId":"default"},"updatedAt":1774386547341,"sessionId":"923f7941-8832-4b11-baab-70573a106770","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":27450,"estimatedCostUsd":0.38644850000000003,"status":"done","startedAt":1774386533004,"endedAt":1774386547314,"runtimeMs":14310,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"whatsapp","lastTo":"120363407571517396@g.us","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\prometeo\\sessions\\923f7941-8832-4b11-baab-70573a106770.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":" Listo. Ya lo dejé persistente en **`AGENTS.md`**.\n\nQuedó guardado como regla operativa:\n- trabajar en `tradelab-front`\n- usar `agent-workspace`\n- commit\n- push\n- PR a `main`\n\nIntenté además dejar commitado ese cambio en mi workspace de OpenClaw, pero ese repo tiene ruido interno/submódulos y no dejó hacer el commit limpio. Igual **la regla sí quedó escrita en `AGENTS.md`**, que era lo importante para que la tome en cuenta.\n\nEn resumen:\n- **sí, ya quedó persistente**\n- **sí, lo voy a tomar como flujo por defecto en TradeLab**","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ceee1298a2a8f9a0169c2fd72f00c8191813e9828e5583bdd\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":570,"output":152,"totalTokens":27602,"cacheRead":26880,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.010425}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774386542636,"responseId":"resp_0ceee1298a2a8f9a0169c2fd71abfc81918e6d17747db01860","__openclaw":{"id":"d251db15","seq":74}}]},{"key":"agent:prometeo:main","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","updatedAt":1774385255725,"sessionId":"c7264268-2e76-4a99-92f9-617f906a785c","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":10289,"estimatedCostUsd":0.056184500000000005,"status":"done","startedAt":1774383567567,"endedAt":1774383572503,"runtimeMs":4936,"abortedLastRun":false,"transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\prometeo\\sessions\\c7264268-2e76-4a99-92f9-617f906a785c.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":""},{"type":"text","text":" Trabajo en `C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\Documents\\tradelab-front`, debo trabajar en la rama `agent-workspace` y los PRs deben ir hacia `main`.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_003938da176d7ef80169c2f869f6648191a6c022bbbb7236ec\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":177,"output":79,"totalTokens":10368,"cacheRead":10112,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.0041554999999999995}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774385252144,"responseId":"resp_003938da176d7ef80169c2f866f1c481919407484294e6cc44","__openclaw":{"id":"5507fc39","seq":10}}]},{"key":"agent:main:tui-58aa22b5-1457-44bd-b48d-a200e23ff599","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","displayName":"openclaw-tui","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1774384542054,"sessionId":"53917618-3bbd-4365-bd2c-7297f83ec358","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":124994,"estimatedCostUsd":3.0613735,"status":"done","startedAt":1774384500412,"endedAt":1774384542029,"runtimeMs":41617,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\53917618-3bbd-4365-bd2c-7297f83ec358.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":" Perfecto. Esa política tiene sentido.\n\nLa convertí en documento persistente en:\n- `workspace/model-routing-policy.md`\n\nY también la guardé en memoria como regla global tuya:\n- **Atlas es el router**\n- **Ollama** para trabajo barato/seguro\n- **Claude Code** como builder por defecto para código\n- **ChatGPT** como thinker por defecto para razonamiento\n- **Opus / GPT-5** solo cuando el caso de verdad lo justifica\n\nImportante:\nlo que hice **ahora mismo** fue dejar la **política base documentada y recordada**.\n\nLo que **todavía faltaría** para que quede totalmente operativo a nivel sistema es una segunda capa:\n1. **inyectarla explícitamente** en las almas / heurísticas de Atlas y los demás agentes\n2. en Prometeo, dejar más explícito que:\n   - código normal → builder\n   - razonamiento técnico → thinker\n   - casos críticos → modelo fuerte\n3. opcionalmente, reflejar esto también en tu mapa operativo/orquestación\n\nO sea:\n- **la política ya quedó escrita y guardada**\n- pero si quieres que quede **totalmente encarnada** en todos los agentes, el siguiente paso es **propagarla a sus almas y playbooks**\n\nY sí: esa es la dirección correcta.  \nEs básicamente pasar de “tenemos agentes” a “tenemos un sistema de enrutamiento de inteligencia”.\n\nSi quieres, lo siguiente lo hago yo:\n- aplicar esta política a **Atlas + Hestia + Ares + Prometeo**\n- de forma corta, clara y sin llenarles el prompt de basura.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_065fabff4ae479b50169c2f599c0508191a0f36cb8e6d8cfda\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":194,"output":356,"totalTokens":125350,"cacheRead":124800,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0.037025}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774384531806,"responseId":"resp_065fabff4ae479b50169c2f59701ec8191b4a81b6bc0a68a3e","__openclaw":{"id":"1ffeb62a","seq":328}}]},{"key":"agent:main:whatsapp:group:120363407571517396@g.us","kind":"group","channel":"whatsapp","displayName":"whatsapp:g-tradelab","deliveryContext":{"channel":"whatsapp","to":"120363407571517396@g.us","accountId":"default"},"updatedAt":1774383778763,"sessionId":"5093db04-8e72-41bb-8b0d-d061d3c264a3","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"lastChannel":"whatsapp","lastTo":"120363407571517396@g.us","lastAccountId":"default","transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\main\\sessions\\5093db04-8e72-41bb-8b0d-d061d3c264a3.jsonl","messages":[]},{"key":"agent:ares:main","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","updatedAt":1774382158184,"sessionId":"ed5aa12d-08d8-42ea-8b15-48e3dbe66030","model":"gpt-5.4","contextTokens":272000,"totalTokens":12207,"estimatedCostUsd":0.08468999999999999,"status":"done","startedAt":1774376948319,"endedAt":1774376951504,"runtimeMs":3185,"abortedLastRun":false,"transcriptPath":"C:\\Users\\Gustavo\\.openclaw\\agents\\ares\\sessions\\ed5aa12d-08d8-42ea-8b15-48e3dbe66030.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":""},{"type":"text","text":" No puedo enviarlo todavía: desde e